---
title: California-Style Turkey and Bacon Burgers with Guacamole and Wedges
description: It’s no secret that we're obsessed with guacamole in the HelloFresh kitchen. It’s the perfect all-purpose creamy topping! We especially love it sandwiched in this fresh Cali-inspired turkey burger.
